column2: SELECT s.plate, s.fiberid, s.mjdz                     FROM  specobj as s, Galaxy as g, SpecPhoto as sph                       WHERE s.class = &&&                      AND s.specobjid = g.specobjid                       AND sph.specobjid = g.specobjid                      AND g.specobjid > #                      AND sph.z > # into MyDB.test
